BC TopLevelNode extension INSTALL

Introduction
============

1. What is the BC TopLevelNode extension?
   ------------------------------------------------

   BC TopLevelNode is a true eZ publish extension that
   provides commandline script to create top level node
   or move a node to the top level root node.

   For more information about this extension please read the README file.

